---
title: Moroccan Honey Beef & Veggie Couscous with Yoghurt, Cherry Tomatoes & Roasted Almonds
description: Everything tastes amazing when glazed in honey and those chermoula beef strips are already too good to resist.
A fluffy couscous with roast veggies seems like the perfect match up to round out this dish.
